ChangeLog for OH2MP ESP32 BLE2MQTT

2021-01-17
	- Fixed bootlooping if config files were unexistent. Should start portal automatically in that case.

2021-01-01
	- Added RSSI to the data
	- Added last half to the MAC address to concat to the default hostname
	- Now the MQTT client disconnects nicely
	- Added watchdog
	- The unit tells desired hostname in DHCP request

2020-12-22
	- Initial release


